including Shenara.

450
00:21:02.460 --> 00:21:05.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When the Third Dynasty
was founded ten years later,

451
00:21:05.660 --> 00:21:08.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
a new group of Klingons
were given the titles

452
00:21:08.139 --> 00:21:11.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the names of the original
Imperial Family...

453
00:21:11.978 --> 00:21:14.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to create the <i>illusion</i>
of an unbroken line.

454
00:21:14.737 --> 00:21:17.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, the woman
that you think of

455
00:21:17.296 --> 00:21:19.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
as your 23rd
maternal grandmother...

456
00:21:19.936 --> 00:21:21.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
