457
00:21:22.549 --> 00:21:25.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Your real ancestor's name
was Karana,

458
00:21:25.534 --> 00:21:28.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
