the Imperial Stables.

459
00:21:28.933 --> 00:21:32.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My grandmother's name
was Shenara.

460
00:21:32.252 --> 00:21:34.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That may be
what's been passed down

461
00:21:34.251 --> 00:21:38.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
