but it has no basis in fact.

462
00:21:38.250 --> 00:21:40.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But who cares about facts?

463
00:21:40.169 --> 00:21:43.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The chronicle says that you have
Imperial blood in your veins,

464
00:21:43.568 --> 00:21:46.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and that's exactly what
we'll keep telling everyone.

465
00:21:49.606 --> 00:21:52.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Continue with the saga.

466
00:21:52.805 --> 00:21:54.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My pleasure.

467
00:21:57.437 --> 00:21:58.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, Major.

468
00:21:58.564 --> 00:22:00.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Is it true Dax is having
a party tomorrow night?

469
00:22:00.244 --> 00:22:01.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
