526
00:24:51.752 --> 00:24:53.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm going to kill Worf.

527
00:24:55.111 --> 00:24:56.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm going to kill Worf.

528
00:24:56.950 --> 00:24:59.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's what I'm going to do.

529
00:24:59.349 --> 00:25:01.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I can see it clearly now.

530
00:25:01.269 --> 00:25:02.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm going to kill him.

531
00:25:03.687 --> 00:25:04.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kill Worf.

532
00:25:04.549 --> 00:25:05.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kill Worf.

533
00:25:05.828 --> 00:25:06.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kill Worf.

