575
00:26:51.236 --> 00:26:52.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anything else?

576
00:26:52.156 --> 00:26:54.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll let you know.

577
00:26:54.356 --> 00:26:55.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
